r Props：通过在组件中传递一个函数作为prop，该函数将用于渲染组件的内容。这个函数可以接收组件需要的数据和方法，并返回React元素。\r\n- Hooks：自定义Hooks，将通用逻辑封装到useXxx函数中，可以在多个组件内使用，常见的像数据请求、表单、防抖节流、拖拽等。","closed_by":null,"reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/420/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hankliu62/interview/issues/420/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"menus":[]},"__N_SSG":true}